data.description:
Discover the perfect blend of charm and space for your family! This home sits on a generous .46-acre lot with a large shed, carport, and a screened patio, ideal for family gatherings and outdoor fun. Inside, the beautifully refinished hardwood floors, stunning tile, and stainless steel appliances give you that new construction feeling.

Not to mention, you're just minutes away from restaurants, schools, and hospitals, making life convenient for your family. And when you're ready to explore, I-95 is less than five minutes down the road. Your family's dream home awaits
